quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,27,"Refti Гұande darngal, O hoynoyayЙ“e, O wi'anaЙ“e: Ko holto kafidaaЙ—i am Й—iin Й—i haЙ“iraynoЙ—on fii mum?" Й“een okkaaЙ“e ganndal mbi'a: "Koyeera on hannde e bone on wonii e heeferЙ“e Й“en"."
  16,28,"ЖҒeen Й“en maleykaaji Й“en hunnata, tooГұuЙ“e ko'e-mun, Й“e werloo jebbilraare, (Й“e mbia): "min ngoonaa- no gollatnooЙ“e ko boni!" -"wonaa non woniri, pellet Alla ko nganduЙ—o ko huuwaynoЙ—on".(ngollatnЙ—on.)"
  16,29,"Naatiree dame Jahannama Й—en luttugol ton. Nge bonii ГұaaЖҙorde wonanВҙde townitiiЙ“e Й“en."
  16,30,"Wi'anee Й“een gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e: "Ko holЙ—uum Joomi mon jippini?" ЖҒe mbi'a: "Ko moЖҙЖҙere". Hono woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙinЙ“e aduna Й—oo moЖҙЖҙere; pellet ko saare laakara nden Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude. nde moЖҙЖҙii saare gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  16,31,"Aljannaaji duumal, heЙ“e naati Й—i, caatli no ila ley majji. Hino woodani Й“e toon kala ko Й“e paaletee; ko wano nii Alla yoЙ“irta gooЕӢЙ—uЙ“e Й“en."
  16,32,"ЖҒeen Й“e maleykaaji Й—i mbarata hara ko Й“e laaЙ“Й“e- Й“e mbi'an [Й“en]: "Kisiyee wonii e mon! Naatiree Aljanna on, sabu ko ngollatnoЙ—on kon".e"
  16,33,"Hara [Й“ee sirkooЙ“e fenna] hino habbitii si wonaa nde maleykaaji Й—i ngarata e maЙ“Й“e, maa yami- roore Joomi maa ndeen ara? Ko wano noon Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e waЙ—irnoo. Alla tooГұaani Й“e; si ko woni, ko ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й“e wonnoo e tooГұuЙ“e."
  16,34,"Boneeji Й—i Й“e huuwi Й—in memi Й“en, kon ko Й“e njalkitatnoo jippii e maЙ“Й“e."